Simply put this into your plugins folder, and it will do it's magic!
    In the configuration, all worlds/arenas/projectiles default to true.
    Simply change any of these to false if you don't want them.
Makes wolves from Mob Arena attack your target when you attack at range.
Makes wolves you have previously tamed and any wolves you end up taming attack targets as well
    This is for outside of Mob Arenas. They do not help if you're in an arena.
Between updates if the config file changes, I will make sure you don't need to delete your
  current config. I will make it check for any differences and add them in.
If your server decides to load RangedWolves before MobArena, use the command "/rw reloadMA", as
  this should rerun the code that sets up the Mob Arena stuff.
    Follow this IMMEDIATELY by "/rw reload" to avoid any errors